<title>Opera&apos;s lightweight themes</title>
<link>http://dev.opera.com/articles/view/operas-lightweight-themes</link>
<author>Chris Mills</author>
<guid isPermaLink="true">http://dev.opera.com/articles/view/operas-lightweight-themes</guid>
<pubDate>Thu, 13 Oct 2011 06:59:31 GMT</pubDate>
<description>Opera 12 brings with it a new lightweight theme system, which sits on top of the default Opera theme/skin and makes simple customisations much easier to achieve. In this article we&#39;ll take a look at how this lightweight system works.</description>
